 but only serving 12 months.\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 341, \"end\": 348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999907913485178, \"rank\": 8.479671002410964e-06, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old was controversially picked for the Dutch Olympic volleyball team in June and arrived in France last week under tight security.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 472, \"end\": 477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9387466964640765, \"rank\": 0.04551505100874153, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8754418869591113, \"rank\": 0.13958934910252987, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His Olympic debut on Sunday at Champs de Mars park under the Eiffel Tower was met with boos from the crowd as he and teammate Matthew Immers lost to Italy.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 606, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mars\", \"score\": 0.9983978838800253, \"rank\": 0.0016042245265744269, \"text\": \"Mars\", \"types\": [\"Q634\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mars\"}, {\"begin\": 714, \"end\": 719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.6410744856448923, \"rank\": 0.5594688470400543, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it has been reported byThe Athleticthat Van de Velde requested to stay off-site for the duration of the Games, away from the thousands of other athletes.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is claimed that the DOC agreed to the arrangement to shield him from public scrutiny and media questioning.\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They (the Dutch Olympic Committee) have put out a statement, they have made it very clear there is a lot of safeguarding going on, special extra safeguarding,\\\" International Olympic Committee spokesman Mark Adams told a news conference in Paris on Saturday.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.997131085126872e-16, \"text\": \"Dutch Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NOC*NSF\"}, {\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"score\": 0.5137413298826524, \"rank\": 0.45833333333321225, \"text\": \"Mark Adams\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\"}, {\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998562998, \"rank\": 1.436796189042892e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The DOC outlined its position last Thursday in a statement, which said: \\\"We are implementing concrete measures to ensure a safe sporting environment for all participants.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These measures include, at the request of Van de Velde, alternative accommodation for Van de Velde and no media contact during his stay in Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1563, \"end\": 1568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998562998, \"rank\": 1.436796189042892e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following Italy's victory over the Dutch team, with scores of 22-20, 19-21, 15-13, Van de Velde left the premises on his own.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1582, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.6410744856448923, \"rank\": 0.5594688470400543, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9387466964640765, \"rank\": 0.04551505100874153, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His next match with Immers is scheduled for 31 July at 15:00 BST against Chilean duo Marco and Esteban Grimalt.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0118772394175559e-12, \"